Package ua.net.freecode.chart

Class Summary
AxisSystem This library supports many axes (up to 16 axes at the top, up to 16 axes at the bottom, up to 16 axes at the left and up to 16 axes at the right).
Chart It is the main class, which you instantiate once for each chart on the web page.
ChartPosition Many items to be placed on the chart require x,y coordinates to place them.
CurvePresentation This class determines many important aspects related to the presentation of each series.
Marker Determines the shape of markers to be placed for each x,y points in your data.
